The paper also focuses on numerical algorithms and scientific computing, which suggests the sub-categories cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) and cs.SC (Scientific Computing). Finally, the paper discusses the performance and efficiency of the system, which could fall under the sub-category cs.LG (Machine Learning).
